---
title: Mild Coconut Beef & Veggie Curry with Garlic Rice
description: This creamy coconut beef curry will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night. It's filled to the brim with bright
veggies and a fragrant garlic rice to soak everything up.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mild-coconut-beef-veggie-curry-379cef6b.jpg
